var c = "pragma solidity ^0.4.0;" 

  "contract SampleContract{"
  "address public owner;" 

  "uint public last_completed_SampleContract;" 

  "constructor() public {" 
    "owner = msg.sender;" 
  "}" 

  "modifier restricted() {" 
    "if (msg.sender == owner) _;" 
  "}" 

  "function setCompleted(uint completed) public restricted {" 
    "last_completed_SampleContract = completed;" 
  "}" 

    "function upgrade(address new_address) public restricted {" 
   " SampleContract upgraded = SampleContract(new_address);" 
    "upgraded.setCompleted(last_completed_SampleContract);" 
  "}" 


  "}" ;




export default ()=>{
  return c.split("\n");
}
